title.narrative: Regional and Municipal Infrastructure Development Project

description.narrative: The objectives of the Project are to: (a) improve the efficiency and reliability of selected municipal infrastructure and service; and (b) assist in restoring infrastructure and services and improving the housing conditions of conflict-affected people in Georgia.
